1
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:12,480
Get out of Dayang Village

2
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,680
Calm down everyone, calm down

3
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,800
Can you listen to me?

4
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,880
Everyone calm down first

5
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,000
Calm down a little

6
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,160
Okay, Yang Gang

7
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,560
