12
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,960
Listen to me, listen to me

13
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:41,880
Listen to me, listen to me, okay?

14
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,800
You all know me, right?

15
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:47,240
I'm Yang Gang, I was a former miner

16
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,400
