20
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:01,040
But after Miss Situ and Shanshui Group came

21
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,680
I saw hope

22
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,640
Because all our mine money is ex

23
