Officials were taking it completely

24
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,160
Miss Seto came this time to make repairs for us

25
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:11,680
To improve our efficiency

26
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,320
And earn more wages

27
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,920
We were all laid off

28
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,360
Where do wages come from?

29
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,840
Yes, we were all laid off

30
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,960
And you still make money

31
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:21,079
Director Xiao is the best for us, Director Xiao is the best

32
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:25,640
Director Xiao is the best

33
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,800
We know what worries you all

34
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,920
Shanshui Group does not want anyone to lose their job

35
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,760
As a token of apology

36
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,880
I have prepared a modest gift for you

37
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,360
I hope you accept it

38
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:44,440
Yes, Miss Seto prepared for every family

39
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,440
A bag of rice

40
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,560
And three bottles of oil

41
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,200
You can receive it directly from the union shortly

42
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,720
Just tell us, will we be laid off or not?

43
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,720
Regarding the issue of employment

44
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,280
We will discuss it carefully

45
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,240
We will definitely give you a satisfactory answer

46
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,680
Yes, I, Yang Gang, guarantee you on my honor

47
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,720
Miss Seto didn't really deceive us

48
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:05,000
So, please be patient and wait a little

49
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,760
Good?

50
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,440
I hope you will give us some time

51
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:10,200
Thank you, thank you

52
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,400
Miss Seto

53
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,040
You asked us to come

54
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,800
Will you give us rewards?

55
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,040
Work to make money

56
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,960
And work hard for the rewards

57
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,840
But you must master your work first

58
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,480
To get rewards

59
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,400
Rest assured, Miss Seto

60
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,320
There is no security that our guard team cannot protect

61
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,200
In addition to security

62
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,520
I want you to do something else

63
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,200
If you do it well, the reward will double

64
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,920
truly? Please say so

65
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,160
As long as you order

66
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,079
We will fight through fire and water

67
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:40,960
We will not hesitate

68
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,840
I want you to go among the people

69
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,120
To promote the benefits of reform

70
