73
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:59,160
Dayang Village Mine is a good mine

74
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:02,240
Previously, because of the old system and old ideas

75
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,640
You were earning a little hard-earned money, weren't you?

76
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:06,640
But after reform, things will be different

77
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:09,880
New technologies will dramatically increase efficiency

78
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,240
When the mine makes profits

79
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,960
Of course you will get a larger share

80
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,280
