81
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,279
Rest assured

82
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:19,720
Shanshui Group will not abandon any of you

83
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,640
I'm sure it will in a few years

84
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:25,840
Every family in Dayang Village will build high-rise buildings and drive cars

85
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,360
truly? Good

86
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,080
I guarantee the job gets done

87
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,880
Look, is it beautiful?

88
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:41,040
All of these were bought for you by Xiao Tianman

89
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,640
Yes, I ordered two pieces from famous brands

90
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,600
One for you

91
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,760
Xiao Mei, tell me honestly

92
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,560
Did Xiao Tianman harass you?

93
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,440
no

94
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,800
He said

95
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,400
He said that appearance is as important to a person as a saddle is to a horse

96
00:04:57,400 --> 00:05:00,200
As his assistant, I must be beautiful and elegant, see

97
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,680
Is it beautiful?

98
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,600
Beautiful

99
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,240
My sister, I've found out

100
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:11,360
