101
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,080
He is a good person

102
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:18,000
You know their faces but you don't know their hearts

103
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,960
You should be more careful

104
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,640
Sister, rest assured

105
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,280
I'm smart

106
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,680
I won't be fooled

107
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,720
Look quickly, do you like these shoes?

108
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,280
What's going on ahead?

109
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,400
During the mountain ritual period, vehicle traffic is prohibited

110
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,120
Come back

111
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,880
They retreated

112
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,840
What happened?

113
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,080
President Xiao

114
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,800
What's going on ahead?

115
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,640
I heard something about a mountain ritual

116
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:42,680
Madam Seto

117
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,720
I'm really sorry

118
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,280
You may not know this

119
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,120
This is a tradition in our village Dayang

120
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:49,000
Every year we close the mountain for worship

121
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,000
To pray to the mountain god to protect the safety of the mine

122
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,240
Close the mountain

123
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,280
We only close it for 15 days

124
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:57,720
Let's let our grandfather, the mountain god, rest for a while

125
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,520
I hope you understand

126
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,440
Since it is a tradition

127
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,880
I can't help but understand

128
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,160
Let's go

129
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,160
Thanks

130
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,240
Xiao Tianman used the mountain ritual as an excuse

131
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,280
