138
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:40,640
Look

139
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,560
Yang Gao Yong

140
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,560
Can I come in?

141
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,840
Please come in

142
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,720
