144
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,800
Good

145
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:12,920
It's like this

146
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:16,880
You've heard about the mountain being closed for rituals, right?

147
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,080
certainly

148
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:21,320
Our village has this tradition of closing the mountain for rituals

149
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,840
But this time it is closed for half a month

150
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,720
It must be a conspiracy from Xiao Tianman

151
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,920
Know

152
