First, we never stole from the mine

164
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:10,040
Secondly, the three of us grew up in Dayang Village

165
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:14,440
Indeed, we know some other methods of mining

166
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,920
if

167
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:20,080
You want us to take you to the mine ourselves?

168
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,720
Isn't it?

169
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:21,880
Is this possible?

170
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,360
maybe

171
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:37,640
Pay attention, why is this road so difficult?

172
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,320
This way is good enough

173
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,480
Other methods are more difficult

174
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,360
Help me

175
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,080
Yang Gang

176
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:57,560
You again and again

177
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,600
Don't value favor

178
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,560
Liao Fei, do you know that you are committing a crime?

179
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,240
What are you doing?

180
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,760
What do you mean?

181
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,480
What do you mean?

182
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:06,520
Security team

183
