190
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:31,880
Let's go

191
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,560
Let's walk down the mountain

192
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:37,680
Du Jing, secure and guard the mine entrance well

193
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,360
Don't let some outlaws take the opportunity to rob the mine

194
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,760
concept

195
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,280
Miss Seto

196
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,240
I just thought about it

197
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:46,720
Because I think

198
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,640
