204
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,880
We are familiar with this area

205
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:57,960
What is your opinion?

206
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,680
Yes, we are all from Dayang Village

207
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:02,960
Let's contribute too

208
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,880
It doesn't matter what the salary is

209
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,040
The important thing is that we get it

210
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,080
